sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Istio as Istio Control Plane
    participant AuthorinoCtrl as Authorino
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless Mode)

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>InferenceService created

    Note over Controller: Determine deployment mode:<br/>KServe Serverless

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Istio Gateway<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    K8sAPI-->>Istio: Resources created (VirtualService, Gateway)
    K8sAPI-->>AuthorinoCtrl: AuthConfig created

    Note over KServeCtrl: KServe watches InferenceService

    KServeCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-knative-dev-v1-service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: mTLS (API Server cert)

    Note over Webhook: Validate Knative Service<br/>for service mesh compatibility

    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result<br/>(Allow/Deny)

    alt Validation Passed
        K8sAPI-->>KServeCtrl: Knative Service created
        Note over KServeCtrl: Knative Serving deploys<br/>predictor pods
    else Validation Failed
        K8sAPI-->>KServeCtrl: Error: Validation failed
    end

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Monitoring and Metrics Collection

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: ServiceMonitor discovered

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics response

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Storage Secret Management

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Secret<br/>Label: opendatahub.io/managed=true<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>Secret created

    Note over Controller: Cache secret for<br/>InferenceService storage config

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService<br/>with storage credentials<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
